```
📈 Sales Retro — {date range}
{verified} verified · {form_leads} ad leads · {paid} paid · {topups} top-ups · {cancels} cancel

ACTIVATED (verified + returned, by quota)
  {email:35}  {Nd} · q {Nx} 🔥  ← only if quota hit
  ...
  Not returning ({N}): {email}, {email}, ...

⚠️ {one-line note about any billing hiccup detected}

CANCELS: {domain}, {domain}, ...

🔥 EXISTING QUOTA HITTERS
  {label} {Nx} · {label} {Nx} · ...

👑 MOST ACTIVE
  {email}  {Nd}
  ...

🐋 BIG FISH
  {Company} — {email} ({signal}) {🚨 if churn-flagged}
  ...

📞 DO THIS WEEK
  1. {VERB} {email} — {why}
  ...
```

Sort activated users by quota hits desc, then active days desc. Verbs: CALL / WIN-BACK / SAVE / NURTURE / WELCOME / UPSELL / CHECK.

